{"word":"ἐπονομάζω","slug":"ἐπονομάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n41814\" key=\"e)ponoma/zw\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἐπονομ-άζω</orth>, <sense id=\"n41814.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">apply</tr_> a word (accus.) <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">as a name</tr_> to a thing (dat.), <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ᾧ γένει κέραμον ἐπωνομάκαμεν</foreign> to which sort we <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">have given the name</tr_> pottery, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg031:60d\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ti.\">Ti.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">60d</biblScope> </bibl> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ᾧ τὸ \" ἔστιν \" ἐπονομάζεις</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg006.perseus-grc1:185c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Tht.\">Tht.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">185c</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πᾶσι ταὐτὸν ἐ. ὄνομα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg008.perseus-grc1:263c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Plt.\">Plt.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">263c</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (reversely, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τίς Ἀλεξάνδρῳ τὸν ἑαυτοῦ βίον ἐπονομάζει καθάπερ Πλάτωνι</foreign>; who <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">dedicates</tr_> his life to <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author></bibl>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">calls</tr_> himself an Alexandrist? <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2001.tlg031:354b\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Them.\">Them.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Or.\">Or.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">31.354b</biblScope> </bibl>):—<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τῇ ἀρχῇ ὕβρις ἐπωνομάσθη</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the name</tr_> insolence <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">was given to</tr_> this rule, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg012:238a\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Phdr.\">Phdr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">238a</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg005.perseus-grc1:404b\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Cra.\">Cra.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">404b</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n41814.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">call by</tr_> a name, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀπὸ τοῦ θεῖν θεοὺς αὐτοὺς ἐπονομάσαι [φαίνονται]</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg005.perseus-grc1:397d\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">397d</biblScope> </bibl> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὰς Μούσας ἀπὸ τοῦ μῶσθαι τὸ ὄνομα τοῦτο ἐ.</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">called</tr_> the Muses <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">by</tr_> this name (viz. Muses), ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg005.perseus-grc1:406a\" default=